Package com.pi4j.io.i2c

Interface I2CBus

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    I2CBusImpl
    public interface I2CBus
    This is abstraction of i2c bus. This interface allows the bus to return i2c device.
    Author:
    Daniel Sendula, refactored by RasPelikan

      • getDevice

        I2CDevice getDevice​(int address)
             throws IOException
        Returns i2c device.
        Parameters:
        address - i2c device's address (7-bit address only: 0-127)
        Returns:
        i2c device
        Throws:
        IOException - thrown in case this bus cannot return i2c device.

      • close

        void close()
    throws IOException
        Closes this bus. This usually means closing underlying file.
        Throws:
        IOException - thrown in case there are problems closing this i2c bus.
